hopobject.body: What's the current interest rate for personal loans? prezzo benzac gel The minutes of the meeting in late July showed some disagreement among Fed officials about the precise timing for trimming $85 billion a month in bond purchases. But they also revealed that "almost all" of the 19 Fed officials at the July meeting said they remained "broadly comfortable" with a tentative timeline of scaling back purchases this year, and ending them by the middle of next year.
